      <title>Pulte确认在Fannie的未来问题中领导FHFA</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/pulte-confirmed-to-lead-fhfa-amid-questions-over-fannie-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比尔·帕特（Bill Pulte）被确认为联邦住房金融机构的董事，因为大多数参议院支持他通过监督房利美（Fannie Mae）和弗雷迪·麦克（Freddie Mac）领导他在美国住房市场中发挥关键作用的机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/pulte-confirmed-to-lead-fhfa-amid-questions-over-fannie-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 20:19:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
